<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>About | ArmouryNet</title>
<style>
  * {
    margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  }

  body {
    color: #fff;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom, #0a0a0a 0%, #000000 100%);
  }

  /* --- Galaxy Background --- */
  body::before {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom, #0d0d0d 0%, #000 100%);
    z-index: -2;
  }

  body::after {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 200%; height: 200%;
    background: transparent url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/stardust.png') repeat;
    opacity: 0.35;
    animation: drift 80s linear infinite;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  @keyframes drift {
    from { transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0); }
    to { transform: translate3d(-500px, -500px, 0); }
  }

  /* --- Header --- */
  header {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 15px 60px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .logo-title {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .logo-title img {
    width: 70px;
    height: auto;
  }

  .logo-title h1 {
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #fff;
  }

  nav a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-left: 30px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  nav a:hover {
    color: #f5f5f5;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px #fff;
  }

  nav .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  nav .btn:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: #fff;
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  /* --- About Section --- */
  .about-section {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 160px auto 60px;
    padding: 50px 60px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    animation: fadeSlide 1.2s ease forwards;
    background: rgba(20,20,20,0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .about-section::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: url('file:///C:/Users/aksha/OneDrive/Desktop/login_page/about_bg.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
    filter: brightness(0.35);
    z-index: 0;
    animation: parallax 40s linear infinite;
  }

  .about-section > * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  @keyframes parallax {
    0% { background-position: center top; }
    50% { background-position: center bottom; }
    100% { background-position: center top; }
  }

  @keyframes fadeSlide {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  }

  .about-section p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #dcdcdc;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .feature-list {
    margin-top: 30px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 25px;
  }

  .feature {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 20px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: featureFade 1s ease forwards;
  }

  .feature:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .feature:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .feature:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.9s; }

  @keyframes featureFade {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px) scale(0.98); }
    50% { opacity: 0.6; transform: translateY(10px) scale(1.02); }
    100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
  }

  .feature:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #ffb347; /* Light orange tone */
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255,179,71,0.4);
    animation: glowPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  @keyframes glowPulse {
    from { text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255,179,71,0.3); }
    to { text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,179,71,0.8); }
  }

  .feature p {
    color: #ccc;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .btn-center {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 35px;
  }

  .btn-center .btn {
    padding: 14px 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 2px solid #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }

  .btn-center .btn:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .motto {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 60px 20px;
    animation: fadeSlide 1s ease forwards;
  }

  .motto h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f5a623;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(245,166,35,0.5);
  }

  .motto p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #aaa;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  @media(max-width:900px){
    header { padding: 15px 30px; }
    .about-section { padding: 40px 30px; margin: 140px 20px 40px; }
    .about-section h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    .feature-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="logo-title">
    <img src="logo.webp" alt="ArmouryNet Logo">
    <h1>ArmouryNet</h1>
  </div>
  <nav>
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="#">About</a>
    <a href="/login" class="btn">Login</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="about-section">
  <h2>About ArmouryNet</h2>
  <p><b>ArmouryNet</b> is an integrated battalion inventory and personnel management system that unifies logistics, accountability, and readiness. Designed to digitize command efficiency, it provides real-time insights and control across all operational layers.</p>

  <div class="feature-list">
    <div class="feature">
      <h3>🎖️ Mission</h3>
      <p>To revolutionize battalion management through automation and transparency — enhancing combat readiness and operational discipline.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <h3>🧭 Core Capabilities</h3>
      <p>• Role-based command dashboards (CO, QM, Adjutant, MTO)<br>
         • Real-time personnel and asset tracking<br>
         • Leave, duty, and logistics synchronization<br>
         • Secure, auditable data system integrated with MySQL backend</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
      <h3>⚔️ Vision</h3>
      <p>To build a trusted, scalable digital infrastructure for every battalion — bridging command leadership with data-driven readiness.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="btn-center">
    <a href="/login" class="btn">Proceed to Login</a>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="motto">
  <h3>“वीर भोग्या वसुंधरा”</h3>
  <p><i>The Brave Shall Inherit the Earth</i></p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
